      "span_text": "At each scheduled postoperative study visit, a full ophthalmic assessment was completed to include slit-lamp biomicroscopy (AE indirect binocular ophthalmoscopy when required) to assess retinal attachment status and PVR grade, [CITATION_1] and parameters including best-corrected visual acuity (VA) (ETDRS chart) applanation tonometry and anterior segment assessment were recorded."
